ed="T" n="0767a01"/><persName key="A010354">釋光瑤</persName>，姓<name>周</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000003795">北京</placeName>人也。幼鍾荼蓼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g905"/>，都不<lb
ed="T" n="0767a02"/>勝情，誓志出家。捨講肆，入禪林，凡嚮宗<lb
ed="T" n="0767a03"/>師，悉從求益。末遭<persName key="A005612">會<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，金<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[鏍-糸+廾]</sic><corr>錍</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="beg0767001"/>抉<anchor xml:id="end0767001"/>瞙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1528"/>，明<lb
ed="T" n="0767a04"/>視十方。後到<placeName key="PL000000022054">沂水蒙山</placeName>，結草成庵，怡然宴<lb
ed="T" n="0767a05"/>坐。<placeName key="PL000000020721">鄶</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000022048">費</placeName>之人翕然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>從化。時<placeName key="PL000000015093">慎邑</placeName>大夫知重，首<lb
ed="T" n="0767a06"/>創禪宮，次<placeName key="PL000000021539">兗州</placeName>節使<persName key="A010362">王僚</persName>尚書躬請入州行<lb
ed="T" n="0767a07"/>化，奏<anchor xml:id="beg0767002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>著</sic><corr>署</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0767002"/>額號<placeName key="PL000000021896">寶真</placeName>。學侶憧憧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1486"/>，多霑大利。<date from-iso="+0807-02-15" key="j20158562016209" to-iso="+0808-02-03">元<lb
ed="T" n="0767a08"/>和<anchor xml:id="beg0767sgsz1"/>二<anchor xml:id="end0767sgsz1"/>年</date>示滅，享年九十二云。又<date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000027105">襄州慈恩<lb
ed="T" n="0767a09"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A010355">釋道堅</persName>，姓王氏，<placeName key="PL000000010986">丹陽</placeName>人也。初發心於<placeName key="PL000000008579"><anchor xml:id="beg0767sgsz2"/>牛<anchor xml:id="end0767sgsz2"/>頭<lb
ed="T" n="0767a10"/>山</placeName><persName key="A010048">慧忠<roleName>禪祖</roleName></persName>。<date from-iso="+0766-12-22" key="j20011912001238" to-iso="+0767-02-07"><name>大曆</name>元年</date>，栖隱<placeName key="PL000000016614">池州南泉山</placeName>。後<lb
ed="T" n="0767a11"/>詣<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄漢</placeName>，泊<placeName key="PL000000027105">慈恩寺</placeName>。<date from-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742015855" to-iso="+0807-02-14"><name>元和</name>初載</date>，相國<persName key="A000047">燕公</persName><ptr target="#n1447"/>鎮<lb
ed="T" n="0767a12"/>于<placeName key="PL000000027117">漢南</placeName><ptr target="#n1448"/>，深相欽重，問道周勤，施供繁沓。遂<lb
ed="T" n="0767a13"/>於<placeName key="PL000000027088">鳳林關</placeName>外造寺請居。<date from-iso="0807" key="j20158562016209">二年</date>示滅，春秋七<lb
ed="T" n="0767a14"/>十三云。</p>
